### 创建一个测试quiz
POST http://localhost:4000/api/courses/RS101/quizzes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Test Quiz",
    "type": "Graded Quiz",
    "points": 100,
    "multipleAttempts": true,
    "numberAttempts": 3,
    "timeLimit": 30,
    "questions": [
        {
            "_id": "q1",
            "title": "Question 1",
            "type": "multipleChoice",
            "points": 50,
            "question": "What is 2+2?",
            "choices": [
                {"_id": "c1", "title": "3"},
                {"_id": "c2", "title": "4"},
                {"_id": "c3", "title": "5"}
            ],
            "answer": "c2"
        },
        {
            "_id": "q2",
            "title": "Question 2",
            "type": "trueFalse",
            "points": 50,
            "question": "Is the sky blue?",
            "answer": "true"
        }
    ]
}

### 第一次尝试 - 全部答对
POST http://localhost:4000/api/courses/RS101/quizzes/QUIZ_ID/attempts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "studentId": "123",
    "startTime": "2024-04-21T10:00:00Z",
    "answers": [
        {
            "questionId": "q1",
            "answer": "c2"
        },
        {
            "questionId": "q2",
            "answer": "true"
        }
    ]
}

