### 获取学生的所有尝试记录
GET http://localhost:4000/api/courses/RS101/quizzes/QUIZ_ID/attempts?studentId=123

### 获取学生的最新尝试记录
GET http://localhost:4000/api/courses/RS101/quizzes/QUIZ_ID/latest-attempt?studentId=123

### 获取特定尝试记录
GET http://localhost:4000/api/courses/RS101/quizzes/QUIZ_ID/attempts/ATTEMPT_ID 